        Lgie Lubrica Doniña, born on March 4, 2005, in Ulag, Prieto-Diaz, Sorsogon, is a 19-year-old woman driven by ambition and personal growth. As the eldest of four children, she has developed perseverance and dedication, qualities that have guided her through life's challenges and aspirations.
      </p>
