    <!-- Family Background Section -->
    <section>
      <h2>Family Background</h2>
      <p>
        The eldest of four children, Lgie grew up in a close-knit family. Her father, Domingo Doniña Jr., is a hardworking fisherman whose efforts sustain the family, while her mother, Liezl Doniña, is a devoted homemaker who instilled in her children the value of discipline and compassion. As the eldest sibling, Lgie embraced her role as a guide and role model for her younger siblings, balancing responsibility with her natural curiosity and determination to succeed.
      </p>
    </section>

