        One of her greatest aspirations is to travel and experience the beauty of the world, particularly the wonders of nature. She envisions herself visiting historical landmarks, scenic destinations, and vibrant cities, learning from diverse cultures and gaining experiences that will enrich her life. For her, traveling represents a way to grow as an individual while taking a step closer to fulfilling her dreams of providing a better future for herself and her family. For Lgie, travel is more than just exploration—it is a journey of self-discovery and a way to deepen her appreciation for life.
      </p>
